FFL.md:
$$\cos\theta
  =\frac{
    \langle{a,b}\rangle
  }{
    ||a||\cdot||b||
  }
  =\frac{
    {{\sum_{i=1}^n}} a_i\cdot b_i
  }{
    \sqrt{\sum_{i=1}^n a_i a_i}
    \sqrt{\sum_{i=1}^n b_i b_i}
  } $$

The angle between two vectors is calculated by finding the <span class="inner">inner product</span> between the first and second vectors and dividing by the length of each then take the arc cosine of that value.
